11
0:00:41.26,000 --> 0:00:44,000
The other is power diffusion,

12
0:00:44.26,000 --> 0:00:46,000
the way power is moving

13
0:00:46.26,000 --> 0:00:48,000
from all states West or East

14
0:00:48.26,000 --> 0:00:51,000
to non-state actors.

15
0:00:51.26,000 --> 0:00:53,000
Those two things

16
0:00:53.26,000 --> 0:00:55,000
are the huge shifts of power

17
0:00:55.26,000 --> 0:00:57,000
in our century.

18
0:00:57.26,000 --> 0:01:,000
