140
0:05:55.26,000 --> 0:05:58,000
defined a great power

141
0:05:58.26,000 --> 0:06:01,000
as a country able to prevail in war.

142
0:06:02.26,000 --> 0:06:04,000
But we need a new narrative

143
0:06:04.26,000 --> 0:06:06,000
